HEADWORD: exerciser
<hw>ex"er*ci`ser</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who exercises.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>one who supervises the exercise of animals, such as
horses or dogs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>a device used for exercising muscles; <as>as, a
thigh <ex>exerciser</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exercisible</ent>⟦br⟧
